---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
---

<Layout 
    title="Privacy Policy | Real BMI"
    description="Read our privacy policy. Real BMI ensures your health data remains private and is never stored on our servers."
>
    <Navbar />
    <main class="pt-40 pb-20 px-6 min-h-screen">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto glass-card p-8 md:p-16 space-y-12 border-2 border-[var(--border)]">
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <a href="/en" class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-[var(--accent)] flex items-center gap-2 hover:translate-x-[-4px] transition-transform">
                    <svg class="w-3 h-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18" /></svg>
                    Return Home
                </a>
                <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black tracking-tighter uppercase text-[var(--foreground)]">Privacy Policy</h1>
                <p class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[var(--accent)]">Your Data, Your Privacy</p>
            </div>

            <div class="prose prose-zinc dark:prose-invert max-w-none text-[var(--muted-foreground)] leading-relaxed space-y-8 text-lg md:text-xl font-bold opacity-70">
                <p>
                    At <span class="text-[var(--foreground)]">Real BMI</span>, we understand that your health data is deeply personal. It's more than just numbers; it's a reflection of your hard work, your goals, and your life.
                </p>
                <p>
                    My commitment to you is absolute: <span class="text-[var(--foreground)] tracking-tight">Your data stays with you.</span> We do not store your height, weight, or age on our servers. The calculations happen instantly on your device, ensuring that your privacy is never a point of compromise.
                </p>
                <p>
                    We only use anonymous analytics to understand how we can make our precision instrument better for everyone. We will never sell, trade, or misuse the trust you place in us when you hit that "Calculate" button.
                </p>
                <div class="pt-8 border-t border-[var(--border)] italic opacity-60 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                    "Trust is the foundation of any health journey. I built this tool to protect yours." — Bhawanshi Dosi
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>
